        	<div class="left span8">
            
            <div class="row-fluid">
			                <article id="post-2538" class="span12 post-2538 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news tag-contracts tag-new-hire tag-schafer tag-vice-president" >
                    
                    <div class="post-type-container span1">
                        <div class="post-type">
                                <i class="big-icon-file "></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="span11">
                                        
                    <div class="post-title row-fluid"><h3><a href="http://www.schafercorp.com/mark-connel-joins-schafer-corporation-as-vpexecutive-director-of-contracts-and-purchasing/">Mark Connel joins Schafer Corporation as VP/Executive Director of Contracts and Purchasing</a></h3></div>
                    <div class="post-header row-fluid">
                            <div class="post-meta row-fluid">
                                <div class="post-date"><i class="icon-calendar"></i>Apr 7, 2016</div>
                                                                <div class="post-category"><i class="icon-folder-open"></i><span><a href="http://www.schafercorp.com/category/news/" title="View all posts in News">News</a></span></div>
                                                                                                
                            </div>
                    </div>
                    
                                        <div class="post-content row-fluid">
                        <div id="attachment_2528" style="width: 160px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><img src="https://www.schafercorp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/MarkConnel.jpg" alt="Mark Connel" width="150" height="188" class="size-full wp-image-2528" /><p class="wp-caption-text"><br />Mark Connel<br /><em>Vice President/Executive Director, Contracts, Subcontracts, and Purchasing</em></p></div><a href="http://www.schafercorp.com/about-us/corporate-leadership-full/#mark-connel">Mark Connel</a> joined Schafer on April 7, 2016 as Vice President/Executive Director of Contracts, Subcontracts, and Purchasing.  Mark has over 30 years of experience in contract and subcontract management leadership.</p>
<p>Prior to joining Schafer, Mark served as Vice President and Executive Director of Contracts for SRA International, Inc., and Senior Vice President for Administration and Director of Contracts &#038; Pricing for the Intelligence and Security (IS&#038;S) Group at Science Applications International Corporation (SAIC). He also held other contract and procurement/subcontract management positions with Boeing Information Services and The Boeing Company in Seattle, WA. Mark is a graduate of the University of Washington (Seattle) and holds advanced degrees from Seattle University (MBA) and Syracuse (MS – Information Management).</p>
                                            </div>
                                        
                     
